<th style="">Documents and statements</th>
<td class="" style="">4 Constitutions:
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Dei_Verbum" title="Dei Verbum">Dei Verbum</a></i> (<i>Dogmatic</i> Constitution on Divine Revelation)</li>
