<li><i><a href="/wiki/Inter_Mirifica" title="Inter Mirifica">Inter Mirifica</a></i> (Social Communication)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Optatam_Totius" title="Optatam Totius">Optatam Totius</a></i> (Priestly Training)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Orientalium_Ecclesiarum" title="Orientalium Ecclesiarum">Orientalium Ecclesiarum</a></i> (Eastern Churches)</li>
