<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Dignitatis_Humanae" title="Dignitatis Humanae">Dignitatis Humanæ</a></i> (Religious Freedom)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Gravissimum_Educationis" title="Gravissimum Educationis">Gravissimum Educationis</a></i> (Christian Education)</li>
