<tr>
<th style=";" colspan="2" class="navbox-title">
<div style="float:left; width:6em;text-align:left;">
<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;;;border:none;; font-size:xx-small;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Ecumenical_councils" title="Template:Ecumenical councils"><span title="View this template" style=";;border:none;">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Ecumenical_councils" title="Template talk:Ecumenical councils"><span title="Discussion about this template" style=";;border:none;">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Ecumenical_councils&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Ecumenical_councils&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";;border:none;;">e</span></a></div>
</div>
<span style="font-size:110%;"><a href="/wiki/Ecumenical_council" title="Ecumenical council">Ecumenical councils</a></span></th>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px;">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Seven recognized in <a href="/wiki/Eastern_Orthodox_Church" title="Eastern Orthodox Church">East</a> and <a href="/wiki/Western_Christianity" title="Western Christianity">West</a></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Nicaea" title="First Council of Nicaea">Nicaea I</a> (325) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Constantinople" title="First Council of Constantinople">Constantinople I</a> (381) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Ephesus" title="First Council of Ephesus">Ephesus</a> (431) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Council_of_Chalcedon" title="Council of Chalcedon">Chalcedon</a> (451) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_Constantinople" title="Second Council of Constantinople">Constantinople II</a> (553) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Third_Council_of_Constantinople" title="Third Council of Constantinople">Constantinople III</a> (680-681) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_Nicaea" title="Second Council of Nicaea">Nicaea II</a> (787)</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Recognized only by <a href="/wiki/Eastern_Orthodox_Church" title="Eastern Orthodox Church">Eastern Orthodox</a><br />
<i>(partly recognized)</i></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Fourth_Council_of_Constantinople_(Eastern_Orthodox)" title="Fourth Council of Constantinople (Eastern Orthodox)">Constantinople IV (879-880)</a><br />
<i>(<a href="/wiki/Quinisext_Council" title="Quinisext Council">Quinisext Council</a> [692] <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Fifth_Council_of_Constantinople" title="Fifth Council of Constantinople">Constantinople V</a> [1341-1351] <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Synod_of_Jerusalem" title="Synod of Jerusalem">Synod of Jerusalem</a> [1672])</i></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Recognized only by <a href="/wiki/Roman_Catholic_Church" title="Roman Catholic Church">Roman Catholic</a></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Fourth_Council_of_Constantinople_(Catholic)" title="Fourth Council of Constantinople (Catholic)">Constantinople IV (869-870)</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_the_Lateran" title="First Council of the Lateran">Lateran I</a> (1123) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_the_Lateran" title="Second Council of the Lateran">Lateran II</a> (1139) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Third_Council_of_the_Lateran" title="Third Council of the Lateran">Lateran III</a> (1179) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Fourth_Council_of_the_Lateran" title="Fourth Council of the Lateran">Lateran IV</a> (1215) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Lyon" title="First Council of Lyon">Lyon I</a> (1245) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_Lyon" title="Second Council of Lyon">Lyon II</a> (1274) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Council_of_Vienne" title="Council of Vienne">Vienne</a> (1311-1312) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Council_of_Constance" title="Council of Constance">Constance</a> (1414-1418) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Council_of_Florence" title="Council of Florence">Basel-Ferrara-Florence</a> (1431-1445) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Fifth_Council_of_the_Lateran" title="Fifth Council of the Lateran">Lateran V</a> (1512-1514)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Council_of_Trent" title="Council of Trent">Trent</a> (1545-1563) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/First_Vatican_Council" title="First Vatican Council">Vatican I</a> (1869-1870) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <strong class="selflink">Vatican II</strong> (1962-1965)</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px;">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-abovebelow" style=";" colspan="2"><a href="/wiki/Anglicanism" title="Anglicanism">Anglicans</a> and most <a href="/wiki/Protestantism" title="Protestantism">Protestant churches</a> accept the first seven Ecumenical Councils.<br />
The <a href="/wiki/Oriental_Orthodoxy" title="Oriental Orthodoxy">Oriental Orthodox</a> accept the first three councils, the <a href="/wiki/Assyrian_Church_of_the_East" title="Assyrian Church of the East">Assyrian Church of the East</a> only the first two.</td>
</tr>
